rMatrix project written by debug.net@gmail.com:

rmatrixb and rain are designed to resemble the same program however with slightly different throughts in mind: rmatrixb is for those with transparent terminals with grayscale backgrounds and themes that wa want a little movement going on in the background. rain is actually a older revision taken to run just the rain stream but no color so that those with limited terminals can have the same experience . intent of the rain program is still open...
